abstract: The inference especially is that black voters, who currently demonstrate little support for the former mayor in polling, would follow the lead of Iowa caucusgoers and rally around him.
snippet: The inference especially is that black voters, who currently demonstrate little support for the former mayor in polling, would follow the lead of Iowa caucusgoers and rally around him.
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES — Top strategists for Pete Buttigieg said they needed a top finish in Iowa on Monday and in New Hampshire the following week, but that first place was not a make-or-break deal for the campaign.

abstract: The Wisconsin Republican Party this week will open its first-ever office in the heart of downtown Milwaukee, one of the clearest signs yet of the party's push to cut into Democrats' advantage among minority voters and the latest indication of how hard-fought every vote will be in the battleground state.

abstract: Senator Amy Klobuchar summed up her final pitch with a geographic appeal.
snippet: Senator Amy Klobuchar summed up her final pitch with a geographic appeal.
lead_paragraph: BETTENDORF — In her first event back in Iowa after spending most of the week tethered to Washington for the impeachment trial, Senator Amy Klobuchar summed up her final pitch with a geographic appeal: the path to a Democratic victory in 2020 is through the Midwest.

abstract: Republican U.S. Senator John Cornyn said the Senate may not make a decision in President Donald Trump's impeachment trial until next week, CNN reported on Friday as senators were due to vote on whether to allow witnesses.
snippet: Republican U.S. Senator John Cornyn said the Senate may not make a decision in President Donald Trump's impeachment trial until next week, CNN reported on Friday as senators were due to vote on whether to allow witnesses.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Republican U.S. Senator John Cornyn said the Senate may not make a decision in President Donald Trump's impeachment trial until next week, CNN reported on Friday as senators were due to vote on whether to allow witnesses.
headline_main: U.S. Senate May Not Decide Trump Impeachment Verdict Until Next Week-CNN
headline_print_headline: U.S. Senate May Not Decide Trump Impeachment Verdict Until Next Week-CNN
